sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Notebook)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Client)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>Ports: 6379, 8265, 10001
    participant Workers as Ray Worker Pods
    participant LocalFS as Local Filesystem<br/>(~/.local/share/codeflare/tls/)
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Gateway: Flow 1: Interactive RayCluster Lifecycle

    User->>SDK: Create ClusterConfiguration<br/> + Cluster objects
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer/OIDC/OAuth
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CR created
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRs<br/>Auth: Service Account
    KubeRay->>HeadPod: Create head pod
    KubeRay->>Workers: Create worker pods
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create CA Secret<br/>({cluster}-ca-secret-{uid})

    SDK->>K8sAPI: Wait for Ready + Read CA Secret<br/>Auth: Bearer/OIDC/OAuth
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA cert + key
    SDK->>LocalFS: Generate client TLS cert/key<br/>(RSA-3072, SHA-256)<br/>File permissions: 0600

    User->>SDK: ray.init(address=...)
    SDK->>HeadPod: gRPC connection<br/>10001/TCP mTLS<br/>Auth: Client certificate
    HeadPod-->>SDK: Connected

    Note over User,Gateway: Flow 2: RayJob Submission with Local Files

    User->>SDK: Create RayJob with<br/>local Python files
    SDK->>LocalFS: Read local files<br/>+ zip working directory
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer/OIDC/OAuth
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Create Secret ({rayjob}-files)<br/>with ownerReference to RayJob<br/>Auth: Bearer/OIDC/OAuth
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CRs
    KubeRay->>HeadPod: Create submitter pod<br/>with Secret volume mount
    HeadPod->>HeadPod: Submit job via<br/>Dashboard API 8265/TCP

    Note over User,Gateway: Flow 3: Dashboard URL Resolution (RHOAI v3.0+)

    SDK->>K8sAPI: List HTTPRoutes<br/>(label: ray.io/cluster-name)<br/>Auth: Bearer/OIDC/OAuth
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: HTTPRoute found
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Get Gateway CR<br/>Auth: Bearer/OIDC/OAuth
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Gateway hostname
    SDK-->>User: Dashboard URL:<br/>https://{hostname}/ray/{ns}/{cluster}
    User->>Gateway: Open Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>HeadPod: Proxy to Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP
    HeadPod-->>Gateway: Dashboard response
    Gateway-->>User: Dashboard UI

    Note over SDK,K8sAPI: Fallback: OpenShift Route → Ingress<br/>if no HTTPRoute found
